cache

private static final java.util.concurrent.ConcurrentHashMap<java.lang.String,Subsystem> cache
Cache for subsystems. The cache optimizes Subsystem creation so that a Subsystem gets created precisely once in each run. It also enables the use of two-way navigable associations that otherwise would create infinite loops of nested DTOs and subsystems.
